This are simple pythin scripts rotating DC motor connected to port M1

Before using this .py you need to download  .C code from Adafruit,
compile it as python egg and install.
This is instruction for the steps above:



Installing software
https://learn.adafruit.com/adafruit-dc-and-stepper-motor-hat-for-raspberry-pi/installing-software



cd /home/pi
git clone https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit-Motor-HAT-Python-Library.git

sudo apt-get install python-dev

#Now install it with the setup install command:
sudo python setup.py install

>>>>
